                            <comment id="77880" author="rhenwood" created="Wed, 26 Feb 2014 00:44:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have just learned there is a Web Help transformation for Docbook:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://docbook.sourceforge.net/release/xsl/1.76.1/webhelp/docs/content/ch02s01.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://docbook.sourceforge.net/release/xsl/1.76.1/webhelp/docs/content/ch02s01.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="62212" author="rhenwood" created="Fri, 12 Jul 2013 19:16:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed a patch to name chunked-html directory.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="62152" author="rhenwood" created="Thu, 11 Jul 2013 19:35:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have just approved: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/5834/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/5834/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have made a subsequent change to create a more suitable directory to contain the chunks:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6943&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6943&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54762" author="rhenwood" created="Mon, 25 Mar 2013 16:01:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for this Przemyslaw.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Another approach is also attacking this problem: Using Publican: &lt;a href=&quot;http://jfearn.fedorapeople.org/en-US/Publican/3.0/html/Users_Guide/index.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://jfearn.fedorapeople.org/en-US/Publican/3.0/html/Users_Guide/index.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This work is begin tracked on:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.hpdd.intel.com/browse/LUDOC-120&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://jira.hpdd.intel.com/browse/LUDOC-120&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54760" author="przemekd" created="Mon, 25 Mar 2013 15:46:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;First try:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,5834&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,5834&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="50487" author="rhenwood" created="Tue, 15 Jan 2013 13:33:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I like this idea. I propose to follow the simple instructions on this page&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sagehill.net/docbookxsl/Chunking.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.sagehill.net/docbookxsl/Chunking.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;FYI: Implementing this in a structured way will require some interaction with sys-admin to create the correct folders automatically on the build server.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
